## Allowed Models

### Claude 4.5 Opus (Anthropic)
- **Context:** 200k tokens
- **Status:** ALLOWED
- **Best for:**
  - Architecture and complex technical decisions
  - Trade-offs (performance vs cost vs maintenance)
  - Before code exists
- **Strength:** Deep thinking, less over-engineering

---

### Claude 4.5 Sonnet (Anthropic)
- **Context:** 200k → 1M tokens
- **Status:** ALLOWED
- **Best for:**
  - Legacy code refactoring
  - Large code reading
  - Incremental adjustments
- **Strength:** Conservative, respects existing code, doesn't break production

---

### GPT-5.2 (OpenAI)
- **Context:** 272k tokens
- **Status:** ALLOWED
- **Best for:**
  - Technical planning
  - Pattern definition
  - Structured documentation
  - Conceptual PR reviews
- **Strength:** Consistency, standardization, technical governance

---

### GPT-5.1 Codex Max (OpenAI)
- **Context:** 272k tokens
- **Status:** ALLOWED
- **Best for:**
  - Code writing
  - APIs
  - Tests
  - Integrations
- **Strength:** Precise execution, less hallucination, ideal for production

---

### Cursor Composer + GPT-5.1 Codex
- **Context:** 200k tokens
- **Status:** ALLOWED (preferred for daily work)
- **Best for:**
  - Daily development
  - Working with real code
  - Incremental evolution
- **Strength:** Repository context, working on code (not just generating)

---

### Gemini 3 Flash (Google)
- **Context:** 200k → 1M tokens
- **Status:** ALLOWED
- **Best for:**
  - Boilerplate
  - Quick scripts
  - Simple conversions
- **Strength:** Extreme speed, low cost
- **Limit:** Not ideal for architectural decisions

---

### Gemini 3 Pro (Google)
- **Context:** 200k → 1M tokens
- **Status:** ALLOWED
- **Best for:**
  - Large codebase analysis
  - Complex debugging
  - Multiple file review
- **Strength:** Massive context reading, good static analysis

---

### Grok Code (xAI)
- **Status:** ALLOWED (with caution)
- **Best for:**
  - Exploring alternatives
  - Questioning decisions
  - Unconventional thinking
- **Strength:** Less aligned, more provocative
- **Limit:** Requires more human validation

